Gala Coral, Playtech Discuss Software Supply Deal, Mail Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-15T18:29:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-15/gala-coral-playtech-discuss-software-supply-deal-mail-reports.html
Gala Coral Group Ltd. is in
discussions with  Playtech Ltd. (PTEC)  about providing the software for
its Internet bingo, sports betting and casino games, the Mail on
Sunday reported, citing unidentified people at the company. The
deal is likely to be a supply agreement and not a joint venture,
the people said, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 